name: dvnmdnss ~ mind
description:
dvnmdnss is a temporary project that seeks to express fundamental realities through electronic music. the work "dualism" consists of two pieces focused on the microhouse, placing organic and synthesized elements in opposite sides.
Body is a track produced through organic samples of bass and percussion, with a more physical proposal, aimed at an energetic dance floor
Mind is a track produced entirely with sound design, a proposal aimed at a more introspective dance floor.
